						 <p>I really really like certain aspects of this. I think the writing itself is rather well done; it feels descriptive yet not overly so to break tone. The fact that it doesn't end with any certainty is both good and bad imo; I would have liked further insight into this entities actions. But overall, I enjoyed what I read.</p> 
